    "This file takes cleaned data and performs all analysis found in Famulari & Goodman (2020). All code in this file is in Stata (version 16).\n",
    "\n",
    "The necessary file structure for this code to work is as follows: \n",
    "- base directory\n",
    "    - jupyter\n",
    "        - analyze_data.ipynb\n",
    "    - data\n",
    "        - generated\n",
    "            - dem_concurrent.csv\n",
    "            - dem_nextquarter.csv\n",
    "            - id-year_level_data.csv\n",
    "    - tex\n",
    "        - plots\n",
    "        - tables"
   ]
  },
