   "source": [
    "## Post-Double-Selection (control var selection)\n",
    "Here we use Belloni, Chernozhukov, and Hansen (2014)'s post-double-selection procedure to choose control variables in a principled manner. The method uses the lasso (least absolute shrinkage and selection operator) to predict, separately, outcomes of interest and treatment indicators. Then, one takes the union of the important covariates and includes them as controls in her specification of interest.\n",
    "\n",
    "Because `pdslasso` and `ivlasso`both produce coefficient estimates, we store these here as well."
   ]
